markets.title: Will DOGE audit Fort Knox before May 2025
markets.rules_primary: If DOGE has initiated an audit of Fort Knox's gold reserves before. May 1, 2025, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: DOGE includes DOGE staff, DOGE teams, and includes other federal government employees that are within a body supervising Fort Knox, e.g. the Department of the Treasury so long as they are reported to be working on the audit under the supervision or direction of DOGE; or Elon Musk. The report must specify that a federal employee working under the direction or supervision of DOGE has made a physical or in-person investigation into the Fort Knox gold reserves in order to be considered an audit.
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if the event occurs.
